Content: Dreaming of a trip to Disneyland Paris? ✨ ⁣⁣🏰 Starting today, gather your fam for the enchanting Disney Symphony of Colours at Sleeping Beauty Castle. The remixed electro-syntho-magnetic music creates a magical tempo for this spectacular festival of night-time joy⁣⁣🎶 Join us on this extraordinary family-friendly event—a magical journey through Disney history that will create lasting memories for all generations! Content: Calling all Disneyland Paris fans!⁣⁣🌈✨ Starting 10th February, gather the fam for A Million Splashes of Colour, a vibrant Disney-Pixar daytime show! 🎬🎶 This lively spectacle, performed daily, explores classics and recent hits, guiding you and your family through the studios' rich storytelling history⁣⁣🎨 Art-inspired floats, brimming with Disney details, promise a delightful trip down memory lane. From giant paintbrushes to oversized paint pots, each float captures the essence of Disney Animation and Pixar, creating a magical experience for families⁣⁣🎵 Immerse your family in this celebration with original scores and iconic songs, from 'The Bare Necessities' to 'You’ve Got a Friend in Me.' Don't miss this enchanting experience that brings Disney Animation and Pixar magic to life! Enjoy until 30th September 2024 🌟⁣⁣#DisneySymphonyOfColours #ElectricalSkyParade #DisneyMagic #DisneylandParis #DisneyParksUK #DisneyUKNews
